window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cheyenne is at the crossroads. Who will sit on the Drow throne? </p> <p>The blight is still ravaging Ambar'og√∫l and spilling through the Border portals into Earth. It's hard enough to discover the secrets in her father's world that will force the Crown to step down. </p> <p>Now Cheyenne has to battle the darkness on both sides of the Border and keep her old life running like normal. </p> <p>With a traitor in the FRoE and war machines tearing through Virginia, who can the halfling trust? Who will get a chance for redemption? </p> <p>Two different worlds are counting on the Goth Drow. What will it take to save them both?</p>"; 
